1dwm 
============================
1dwm is a fork of the *brilliant* dwm by suckless focused on raw speed.


Requirements
------------
In order to build 1dwm you need the Xlib header files.


Installation
------------
Run the following command to build and install 1dwm:

    sudo make clean install

Running dwm
-----------
Add the following line to your .xinitrc to start dwm using startx:

    exec dwm
